Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: 10 Chandler is located along the I-10 Freeway, just north of the Loop 202. Three full-diamond interchanges, one at I-10 at Ray Road, one at I-10 and Chandler Blvd., and the third at Loop 202 at Kyrene Road, provide easy access to the park for visitors traveling from any direction.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: 10 Chandler is a ±553,000 sq. ft. Class A industrial/flex office park comprised on nine buildings located on 37 acres in Chandler, AZ. Centrally located in the Southeast Valley’s premiere business and technology corridor, 10 Chandler has unsurpassed visibility with nearly 1,150 ft. of frontage along Interstate 10 and direct access through two full diamond interchanges. 10 Chandler benefits from its functional design, clear heights up to 26 ft. and generous parking. It is adjacent to great restaurants, shopping, business and entertainment amenities.
